{"tid":1318223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日佢地一定咬住手指狗同電梯狗件事唔放","createTime":"2019-07-15T01:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T03:53:48.000Z","uid":39205,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"88fe2c37b1315564ec7b616e052064d90aaadfb4","tid":1318223,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:47:08.000Z","msg":"今朝食同老母食早餐，佢話琴晚有警察斷左隻手指喎，本身第一句想應佢抵死，但係醒起起身見到有個post有哂相係黑警插眼先，即刻開出黎比老母睇，仲要大大聲咁講：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係喎！我上網睇係個警察想挖佢隻眼先比人咬架喎！</span></span>隔離個呀叔都伸左個頭過黎望一望，再細細聲同佢老婆講。<br />\n<br />\n已經預計到今日黑警page甚至一班藍絲page將會無限放大呢兩件事，始終今次唔同前幾日啲黑警啲𠝹手相咖哩雞相咁一睇就遇左比人笑，啲淺藍淺黃未必咁易接觸到事實嘅全部，所以想大家準備一下，統一放哂啲證據出黎出黎，將真相傳出去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vAatdWm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvAatdWm.png&h=224830d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n『還原甩手指真相』快睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316903</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n極重要!!!!!![正視聽]唔該大家唔好再屈義士主動咬斷隻狗嘅手指<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1317565</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n至於電梯狗今朝睇過好似得一條佢追住人打嘅片(成日睇到一半又忍唔住睇埋佢比圍個段)，如果大家有多啲亦都可以放出黎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/303668637132303/posts/523716915127473?s=1000124775&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmwa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F303668637132303%2Fposts%2F523716915127473%3Fs%3D1000124775%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dxmwa&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=763694fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/303668637132303/posts/523716915127473?s=1000124775&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmwa</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個有被打落電梯嘅前一段<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1317881</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n同時亦都可以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講下黑警係九點幾十點最多人食完飯準備走嘅時候衝入商場</span></span>，嚇親幾多無辜嘅市民，同啲淺黃淺藍講，你諗下你好地地係商場入面呀同個乖仔乖孫食完飯，無啦啦成隊軍隊衝入黎見到你個乖孫係後生仔就打，無陰公呀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/af2jkCC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faf2jkCC.png&h=b484b476&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpnWnQX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpnWnQX.png&h=de499484&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed1e75460a6b4459a03920287da338c2f1d6d0de","tid":1318223,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"大家又多啲相都要send出黎準備send哂比啲老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9135c0c989e88fde1b7204ffa24fe1bda69ee4d9","tid":1318223,"uid":69810,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:48:39.000Z","msg":"我媽話: 俾人插眼何止咬佢手指呀？手我都咬甩佢！<br />\n<br />\n勇武勇武"},{"pid":"85f5f53cbfaf406e01c7d4e6e9873d65ff91ad31","tid":1318223,"uid":39205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:49:37.000Z","msg":"我要佢地成為過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247e61f482f25f0853801148ffa613afc7aeb990","tid":1318223,"uid":69810,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UcKtYq6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUcKtYq6.png&h=d6c3bdc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"517324d0d2e37f83fb2e366f44abd36bc3077a97","tid":1318223,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s